-- Aker Solutions, Matasis Start Company Targeting Metals and Energy Markets
-- B y   M a r i a n n e   S t i g s e t
-- 2010-10-11T11:28:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/aker-solutions-matasis-start-company-targeting-metals-and-energy-markets.html
Aker Solutions ASA and the South
African investment company Matasis Investment Holdings have
formed a new incorporated company named Aker Solutions Matasis,
based in Bryanston, Johannesburg.  Aker Solutions will hold 74 percent and Matasis 26 percent
ownership in the company, which will target the energy and
metals markets offering project management, design, engineering
and construction management services for major projects.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marianne Stigset at 
 mstigset@bloomberg.net  